r.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-53-2023-09-19-17-11-18/6.mp3","time_start":12.94,"time_end":15.59},{"position":7,"content":"I promised a coworker that I'd cover his Sunday shift.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-53-2023-09-19-17-11-18/7.mp3","time_start":15.59,"time_end":18.51},{"position":8,"content":"How much does the tour cost anyway?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-53-2023-09-19-17-11-18/8.mp3","time_start":18.51,"time_end":20.63},{"position":9,"content":"Well, the sightseeing pass is $180.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-53-2023-09-19-17-11-18/9.mp3","time_start":20.8,"time_end":24.77},{"position":10,"content":"I've got the booklet.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-53-2023-09-19-17-11-18/10.mp3","time_start":24.77,"time_end":26.0},{"position":11,"content":"Here, take a look!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-53-2023-09-19-17-11-18/11.mp3","time_start":26.0,"time_end":27.66},{"position":12,"content":"You know it's not too late to change your mind.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-53-2023-09-19-17-11-18/12.mp3","time_start":27.66,"time_end":30.27}]}